q=A.kw(A.b([a1,a2],p),A.b([a3,a4],p),"Ahome is a rental platform that enables users to find, filter, and book apartments directly from property owners in Vietnam, with features such as OTP authentication, advanced search, room management, and issue reporting.","Ahome l\xe0 n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng cho thu\xea gi\xfap ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\xf9ng t\xecm ki\u1ebfm, l\u1ecdc v\xe0 \u0111\u1eb7t ph\xf2ng tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp t\u1eeb ch\u1ee7 nh\xe0 t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam, v\u1edbi c\xe1c t\xednh n\u0103ng nh\u01b0 x\xe1c th\u1ef1c OTP, t\xecm ki\u1ebfm n\xe2ng cao, qu\u1ea3n l\xfd ph\xf2ng v\xe0 b\xe1o c\xe1o s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1.","assets/ahome.png",o,n,"Ahome","https://apps.apple.com/vn/app/homevn-tr%E1%BB%8D-ch%C3%ADnh-ch%E1%BB%A7/id6736515000?l=vi","https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=vn.xtel.ahome.timtro&hl=vi",g,a0,q)
